# Vitality Base — environment variables.
#
# The base runs with NONE of these — tile data is saved in your browser.
#
# --- Optional: cross-device sync (see supabase/sync.sql) ---
# Add your OWN free Supabase project's two PUBLIC keys to sync tile data across
# devices (build on your laptop, see it on your phone). Both are safe in the
# browser. From Supabase → Project Settings → API.
#   1. Create a Supabase project
#   2. Run supabase/sync.sql in its SQL Editor (creates the tile_data table)
#   3. Set these two in Vercel → Settings → Environment Variables, then redeploy
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
